Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:18.94,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You hold your breath to make it through\Nthe bewildering day that confronts you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:25.11,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what this is, don't you?\NWhat do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.14,0:02:31.70,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The pain from shrugging\Nit all off as nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:37.62,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,urges you on enough to be encouraging
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:44.17,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Catching hold but making a mess,\Nwe're still inadequate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:52.20,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but as long as we can forge\Nour shining, unseen future selves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:03:00.65,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Awaken and run where it takes you,\Nleaving mirages behind
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:07.19,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Run with your desire to change,\Nfrom your comfort zone into freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:14.62,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Start choosing between now\Nand the brilliance you can attain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:22.65,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Unaware of your destination,\Ndeep breaths following shallow ones
