Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.89,0:20:10.52,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Road Closed
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.29,0:24:33.29,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,This situation is an unscientific\Nmontage of emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.93,0:24:36.57,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is calling whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.60,0:24:42.49,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Your gaze darts away when I turn around\N(I can feel it)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.52,0:24:44.78,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unkind to tell me I'm imagining things
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.81,0:24:50.29,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,They say having\Nantennas is a talent, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.32,0:24:55.38,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean I want to know\N(I mean) (don't you?)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.41,0:25:02.18,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn up the heat on your youth\Nfor you now, while there's time
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.21,0:25:06.85,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can solve this tomorrow,\Nwhy not solve it right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.88,0:25:12.44,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to solve your mystery
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.47,0:25:17.15,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Track down that secretive boyish figure!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.18,0:25:24.74,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Today) you are a fantasy,\Ndrawing me to you, no fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.77,0:25:30.33,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My curiosity is expanding,\Nlack of tricks notwithstanding
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.36,0:25:37.28,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fascinated, and I have to know, why?
